                            </div>
                            <div class="odes-slide">
                                <img src="/odes_crm/static/description/Inventory.jpeg" alt=""/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="odes-slide">
                                <img src="/odes_crm/static/description/inventory2.jpeg" alt=""/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="odes-slide">
                                <img src="/odes_crm/static/description/inven.jpeg" alt=""/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="odes-navigation-auto">
                                <div class="odes-auto-btn1"></div>
                                <div class="odes-auto-btn2"></div>
                                <div class="odes-auto-btn3"></div>
                                <div class="odes-auto-btn4"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="odes-navigation-manual">
                            <label for="odes-radio1" class="odes-manual-btn"></label>
                            <label for="odes-radio2" class="odes-manual-btn"></label>
                            <label for="odes-radio3" class="odes-manual-btn"></label>
                            <label for="odes-radio4" class="odes-manual-btn"></label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="odes-content">
                        <div class="odes-left-content">
                            <div>
                                <p>Your digital transformation journey has just begun, and I hope that you are as excited as we are!</p>
                                <p>Below, you will find the link to download our comprehensive and concise guide to optimising your inventory management through digital transformation.</p>
                                <p>Our friendly consultants are always happy to give you a free demo of our solution with no obligations.</p>
                                <p>All you have to do is to fill in the form to book a free demo session that will be conducted virtually at your convenience. </p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <a href="/odes_crm/static/description/test.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><button type="button" class="odes-button odes-button-download-guide"><span>Download Guide</span></button></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="odes-right-content">
                            <form action="/campaign-landing-page/success" method="post">
                                <span class="odes-title-form">Schedule a Demo</span>
                                <div class="odes-form-info-selection">
                                    <div class="odes-form-info-selection-date">
                                        <span class="odes-form-info-selection-text">Preferred Date to call</span>
                                        <div class="form-group">
                                            <div class="input-group datetime odes-input-group-date" id="datetimepickerID" data-target-input="nearest">
                                                <input type="date" class="form-control datetimepicker-input odes-input-group-date" name="preferred_date" required=""/>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="odes-form-info-selection-time">
                                        <span class="odes-form-info-selection-text">Preferred Time to call</span>
                                        <div class="odes-select">
                                            <select class="form-control odes-input-group-time" name="preferred_time">
                                                <option t-attf-value="9am_to_12pm" selected="">09.00 AM - 12.00 PM</option>
                                                <option t-attf-value="12pm_to_3pm">12.00 PM - 03.00 PM</option>
                                                <option t-attf-value="3pm_to_6pm">03.00 PM - 06.00 PM</option>
                                            </select>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="odes-form-info">
                                    <div class="odes-form-info-value">
                                        <span>Name</span>
                                        <span>:</span>
                                        <span><t t-esc="name"/></span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="odes-form-info-value">
                                        <span>Email</span>
                                        <span>:</span>
                                        <span><t t-esc="email"/></span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="odes-form-info-value">
                                        <span>Phone</span>
                                        <span>:</span>
                                        <span><t t-esc="phone"/></span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="odes-form-info-value">
                                        <span>Company</span>
                                        <span>:</span>
                                        <span><t t-esc="company"/></span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="odes-form-info-value">
                                        <span>Position</span>
                                        <span>:</span>
                                        <span><t t-esc="position"/></span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <input type="hidden" name="name" t-att-value="name"/>
                                <input type="hidden" name="email" t-att-value="email"/>
                                <input type="hidden" name="phone" t-att-value="phone"/>
                                <input type="hidden" name="position" t-att-value="position"/>
                                <input type="hidden" name="company" t-att-value="company"/>
                                <input type="hidden" name="lead_id" t-att-value="lead_id"/>
                                <input type="hidden" name="contact_id" t-att-value="contact_id"/>
                                <button type="submit" class="odes-button odes-button-book-demo"><span>Book Demo</span></button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <script type="text/javascript">
                    var counter = 1;
                    setInterval(function(){
                        let element = document.getElementById('odes-radio' + counter);
                        if (element){
                            element.checked = true;
                        }
                        counter++;
                        if(counter > 4){
                            counter = 1;
                        }
                    }, 5000);
                </script>
                <section class="s_process_steps pt24 pb24 o_colored_level" data-snippet="s_process_steps" data-name="Steps">
                    <div class="row no-gutters">
                        <div class="col-lg-4 s_process_step pt24 pb24 o_colored_level">
                            <div class="s_process_step_icon">
                                <span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-user-plus fa-2x mx-auto rounded-circle odes-bg-inactive"/>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="s_process_step_content text-center">
                                <h2 class="o_default_snippet_text">Sign Up</h2>
                                <!-- <p class="o_default_snippet_text">Let your customers follow <br/>and understand your process.</p> -->
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4 s_process_step pt24 pb24 o_colored_level">
                            <div class="s_process_step_icon">
                                <span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-download fa-2x mx-auto rounded-circle bg-o-color-5 odes-bg-active"/>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="s_process_step_content text-center">
                                <h2 class="o_default_snippet_text">Download</h2>
                                <!-- <p>Click on the icon to adapt it <br/>to your purpose.</p> -->
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4 s_process_step pt24 pb24 o_colored_level">
                            <div class="s_process_step_icon">
                                <span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-calendar fa-2x mx-auto rounded-circle bg-secondary odes-bg-inactive"/>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="s_process_step_content text-center">
                                <h2 class="o_default_snippet_text">Schedule Demo</h2>
                                <!-- <p class="o_default_snippet_text">Duplicate blocks <br/>to add more steps.</p> -->
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </t>
    </template>

